room_title: Escape room "Prison Break" by Rush To Escape in Las Vegas
room_address: 2185 E Windmill LN Suite 300 Las Vegas, NV 89123
room_description: You are sentenced to life in a maximum security prison. With all appeal requests denied, your only path to freedom is to escape. A sudden riot provides the perfect opportunity. You know that the guard will take control of the riot in 60 minutes. Can you use the elements in your prison cell to break free, or will you and your cellmates spend the rest of your days behind bars?
